2002-06-12  M.L. <m.l@compaqnet.fr>

		Version++ (1.70)
		You need to patch /etc/openwebmail.conf and add:
			"dbm_ext                 .db"
			"dbmopen_ext             .none"
		A patch is applied to /usr/share/httpd/cgi-bin/openwebmail/openwebmail-shared.pl in DBMTEST section to skip dbm tests at startup... (OWM test fails, I can't figure out why).
	
